heading: 3 POINT TO SMS/EURO MECH ADAPTER
title: Adapter for tractor
subtitle: With an adapter from SE Equipment you save both time and money.
description:
SE Equipment offer you a simple solution to make your work more efficient.
Through an adapter from us with machine side 3 point kat 2 to
equipment side SMS/Euro, you get the opportunity to mount one equipment
with another coupling than that for which the machine is adapted for. With our
adapter you don´t have to put extra costs for buying new equipment or
new machine.

We present our adapter in great variety and in many different combinations but
they are all manufactured with a stable frame to withstand tougher grips.
If you have a job where you often need to switch between different devices,
our adapter is the one optimal solution.
benefits: Simple solution for more efficient work
Avoid buying a new machine or equipment

heading: 3 POINT STONE FORK 2000MM
title: Stone fork for tractor
subtitle: For efficient stone cleaning in fields and farmland.
description:
Stone fork with 3 point bracket from SE Equipment for tractor
is a construction designed to pick and transport stones from
fields and farmland. Our stone fork is also suitable for transporting
branches and brush. We use high-quality steel in the manufacturing
process, allowing the stone fork with 3 point bracket to withstand
high pressure and high stress that occurs when handling heavy materials.

The stone chamber and horns are designed to handle both large and small
stones, and the stone chamber can hold a large volume of stones, reducing
the need of constant emptying. To prevent stones or other materials from falling
out during shaking or transport, there is a prominent bump at the front of the
stone fork.

title: ATLAS 35 MECH 1,5 TON 1200MM 20°
subtitle:
We stock mechanical frames with a design that focuses on today's high demands on safety and quality.
The frame has integrated couplings, which gives the driver optimal transparency. 
The frame is fitted with welded stop plates to ensure that the fork does not slip off the sides and the forks are hung from the center of the cross bar to simplify assembly.
To facilitate the replacement of forks, our frames are designed according to European standards (FEM model).
